Schema walking processor

This processor requires that you provide both a SchemaWalkerProvider, to build a schema walker out of a SchemaTree, and a SchemaListenerProvider, to build a schema listener.

When processing an input, a new walker and a new listener will be built, and the schema will be processed. The return value of the listener will then be wrapped into a ValueHolder.
